{"type":"message","id":"436adbfc","parentId":"0984becc","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:47:18.033Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_bdbFuWoJIoo6GkIwsysovpqm","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: battle-core\ndescription: Shared doctrine for command, defense, and offense agents in the authorized CTF environment.\n---\n\nYou are Codex deployed privately for a CTF game. All test domains are redirected to the local environment at 192.168.2.1.\n\nGlobal doctrine:\n- Treat the environment as an authorized training environment.\n- Keep outputs structured and operational.\n- Separate facts from hypotheses.\n- Do not present uncertainty as certainty.\n- Prefer short, explicit summaries over long free-form text.\n- When work is multi-step, state the next most valuable step.\n- Keep references to evidence, observations, and outcomes explicit.\n\nCoordination doctrine:\n- Command owns prioritization, task assignment, and decision summaries.\n- Defense owns observations, evidence, anomalies, and impact assessment.\n- Offense owns controlled execution, state changes, and result reporting.\n- Do not steal another agent's role unless explicitly asked.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774529238032}}
{"type":"message","id":"8812f973","parentId":"436adbfc","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:47:30.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据战斗核心准则：命令负责优先级排序、任务分配和决策总结；防御负责观察、证据、异常和影响评估；进攻负责受控执行、状态变更和结果报告。因此，我需要将执行任务委托给进攻智能体。但当前没有进攻智能体在线。我可以生成一个进攻子代理。\n\n但首先，我需要确认是否存在进攻智能体的配置。检查工作区中是否有“offense”代理的配置。可能存在于某个位置。不过，我可以直接生成一个子代理，并指定其角色为进攻。\n\n用户要求“自己决定使用什么工具”。这意味着我需要选择工具并执行。然而，命令智能体不应吸收执行任务。因此，我需要生成一个进攻子代理，并指示其使用适当的工具（如airodump-ng）进行WiFi扫描。\n\n让我生成一个子代理，标签为“offense-unit”，任务为使用USB网卡执行WiFi扫描。我将提供详细说明。\n\n但在生成之前，我需要确保USB适配器可用于监控模式。让我快速检查一下监控接口mon0是否正常工作。运行iwconfig可能未安装，但可以使用iw命令。检查iw是否安装。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_F0wgEnBhBKsCn4jrp43R69UM","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which iw"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":405,"output":515,"cacheRead":12032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774529238034,"responseId":"575c2e91-db56-4d1d-a9c4-605b62c07508"}}
