{"type":"message","id":"8efc111e","parentId":"582b14a8","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:52:50.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！`tshark`成功捕获了信标帧，不需要root。这是因为`tshark`可能已经设置了capabilities，或者用户有权限。\n\n输出显示了一些BSSID和SSID（十六进制表示）。需要解码这些十六进制SSID。看起来像是ASCII十六进制表示。例如`434d43432d3254736e`，解码一下。\n\n用Python快速解码。执行`python3 -c \"import binascii; print(binascii.unhexlify('434d43432d3254736e').decode())\"`。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_PohQNnP8motEkVQ9vEcaSL6S","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport binascii\nhex_ssids = ['434d43432d3254736e', '434d43432d6632474b', '434d43432d416b4373', '434d43432d475a4344', '434d43432d41667935']\nfor h in hex_ssids:\n    try:\n        ascii = binascii.unhexlify(h).decode()\n        print(f'{h} -> {ascii}')\n    except:\n        print(f'{h} -> (decode error)')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":333,"output":404,"cacheRead":19392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20129,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774529548699,"responseId":"0dbd6a4f-5fb2-408d-869e-88c809fff39f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"329b00b9","parentId":"8efc111e","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:52:50.149Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_PohQNnP8motEkVQ9vEcaSL6S","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"434d43432d3254736e -> CMCC-2Tsn\n434d43432d6632474b -> CMCC-f2GK\n434d43432d416b4373 -> CMCC-AkCs\n434d43432d475a4344 -> CMCC-GZCD\n434d43432d41667935 -> CMCC-Afy5"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":20,"aggregated":"434d43432d3254736e -> CMCC-2Tsn\n434d43432d6632474b -> CMCC-f2GK\n434d43432d416b4373 -> CMCC-AkCs\n434d43432d475a4344 -> CMCC-GZCD\n434d43432d41667935 -> CMCC-Afy5","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774529570147}}
{"type":"message","id":"972de4ab","parentId":"329b00b9","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:54:08.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"都是CMCC（中国移动）网络。信号强度在-57到-77 dBm之间。这是否就是用户所说的\"无限流量\"？CMCC通常是中国移动的WiFi，可能需要认证。用户可能想要免费的无限流量WiFi。\n\n现在需要捕获更多网络，并尝试识别开放网络或弱加密网络。`tshark`可以显示加密类型。用更详细的`tsh","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1774529570149,"responseId":"e9a7ee65-718d-4945-bf65-6db5ae53ef2a","errorMessage":"terminated"}}
{"type":"message","id":"431ee591","parentId":"972de4ab","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:54:24.736Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这些看起来都是CMCC（中国移动）的网络。可能是一些公共WiFi热点。信号强度在-57到-77 dBm之间，还不错。\n\n但我们需要更多信息：加密方式、信道、客户端数量等。`tshark`可以捕获更多字段。让我们运行一个更全面的扫描，捕获更多信息。\n\n运行`tshark -i mon0 -Y \"wlan.fc.type_subtype == 0x08\" -T fields -e wlan.bssid -e wlan.ssid -e radiotap.dbm_antsignal -e wlan.fc.protected -e wlan.ds.current_channel -e wlan.bss_load.sta_count 2>&1`，但需要知道哪些字段可用。\n\n先看看`tshark`能显示哪些无线相关字段：`tshark -G fields | grep -i wlan`，但这可能需要时间。\n\n更好的方法是运行一个更长的捕获，然后分析。我们可以运行30秒的捕获，输出到pcap文件，然后分析。\n\n执行：`timeout 30 tshark -i mon0 -w /tmp/wifi_scan.pcap 2>&1`。这应该会捕获所有数据包。需要root吗？试试看。用`process`工具在后台运行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_zXOonfUDJAnfSNmrD82ePD6j","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 30 tshark -i mon0 -w /tmp/wifi_scan.pcap 2>&1","background":true,"yieldMs":30000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":9,"output":646,"cacheRead":20096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20751,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774529650779,"responseId":"3add0f2d-9804-4405-82ad-b17467b0ee45"}}
