{"type":"message","id":"1e6f956e","parentId":"8e573054","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:54:34.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"等30秒。在此期间，可以准备分析脚本。30秒后，用`process poll`检查状态。现在先等一会儿。\n\n另外，可以考虑同时运行一个更详细的扫描，使用`airodump-ng`，但需要root。也许用户有sudo密码，但不想手动输入。我们可以尝试用`echo \"password\" | sudo -S`，但这样不安全，而且我们不知道密码。\n\n最好还是依赖`tshark`捕获。\n\n等待30秒。同时，可以检查是否有其他工具，如`kismet`或`wifite`，但那些也需要root。\n\n30秒后，分析pcap文件。\n\n现在，先轮询进程状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5P6BNStPVcnUhwLIevnWdCue","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"keen-pine","timeout":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":433,"output":362,"cacheRead":20096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20891,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774529664747,"responseId":"901fdf3f-aea2-4643-a1a4-d3f8f0415e48"}}
