{"type":"message","id":"b38a7be2","parentId":"e717bd22","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:56:42.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"输出显示`wlan.fc.protected`字段为`False`，这意味着这些网络没有加密？但CMCC网络通常需要网页认证，可能使用开放加密但需要门户网站。不过，`wlan.fc.protected`为`False`表示没有WEP/WPA加密。这些可能是开放网络。\n\n但还有一些SSID是十六进制，比如`363138efbc8866616b65efbc89`，解码一下。\n\n运行解码命令。用Python解码所有唯一的SSID。先提取唯一SSID。用`awk`提取第二列，排序去重。执行命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_V1wcReXfCGGSUTmJINluzZEj","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tshark -r /tmp/wifi_scan.pcap -Y \"wlan.fc.type_subtype == 0x08\" -T fields -e wlan.ssid 2>&1 | sort -u | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":853,"output":346,"cacheRead":21248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22447,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774529793404,"responseId":"db416ad8-31d3-4d0d-9db1-38317ebeddb2"}}
