{"type":"message","id":"14f3c9a7","parentId":"aa5022fe","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:56:55.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"只有五个网络。解码这些十六进制字符串。\n\n用Python脚本解码。执行：`python3 -c \"import binascii; ssids=['363138efbc8866616b65efbc89','434d43432d3254736e','434d43432d41667935','434d43432d416b4373','434d43432d6632474b']; for h in ssids: try: print(h, '->', binascii.unhexlify(h).decode('utf-8')); except: print(h, '-> (decode error)')\"`。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_cLfcvTQLBYPERevqCeHKhO1x","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport binascii\nssids = [\n    '363138efbc8866616b65efbc89',\n    '434d43432d3254736e',\n    '434d43432d41667935',\n    '434d43432d416b4373',\n    '434d43432d6632474b'\n]\nfor h in ssids:\n    try:\n        decoded = binascii.unhexlify(h).decode('utf-8')\n        print(f'{h} -> {decoded}')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'{h} -> (decode error: {e})')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":308,"output":435,"cacheRead":22080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22823,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774529802996,"responseId":"834699d3-8842-4885-bff0-5768ce932f10"}}
