{"type":"message","id":"727efca6","parentId":"98138196","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:18:34.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要密码。那么目前我们只能使用非root工具。让我们用tshark进行更长时间的扫描，并编写一个Python脚本来实时分析数据，寻找目标SSID。\n\n我需要创建一个实时的监控脚本。但首先，让我启动一个tshark捕获，然后使用Python处理输出。用管道将tshark输出传递给Python脚本。\n\n让我写一个Python脚本，从标准输入读取tshark输出，解码SSID并检查是否匹配目标。先创建脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_hnl6DV4RbSF34rZypemzG4NG","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/find_target_ssid.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport sys\nimport binascii\n\n# 目标SSID和其十六进制表示\ntarget_ssid = '无限流量+QQ723498873'\ntarget_hex = 'e697a0e99990e6b581e9878f2b5151373233343938383733'\ntarget_partial = 'e697a0e99990e6b581e9878f'  # 仅\"无限流量\"\n\nprint(f\"搜索目标SSID: {target_ssid}\", file=sys.stderr)\nprint(f\"目标十六进制: {target_hex}\", file=sys.stderr)\nprint(\"监听标准输入中的tshark输出...\", file=sys.stderr)\n\nfound = False\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    line = line.strip()\n    if not line:\n        continue\n    \n    # tshark输出可能是十六进制SSID\n    ssid_hex = line\n    \n    # 尝试解码\n    try:\n        # 先尝试直接匹配十六进制\n        if target_hex.lower() in ssid_hex.lower():\n            print(f\"发现完全匹配: {ssid_hex}\")\n            found = True\n            break\n        \n        if target_partial.lower() in ssid_hex.lower():\n            print(f\"发现部分匹配(无限流量): {ssid_hex}\")\n            found = True\n            # 继续检查完整解码\n        \n        # 尝试解码\n        try:\n            decoded = binascii.unhexlify(ssid_hex).decode('utf-8', errors='ignore')\n            if target_ssid in decoded:\n                print(f\"发现解码匹配: {decoded} (原始: {ssid_hex})\")\n                found = True\n                break\n            elif '无限流量' in decoded:\n                print(f\"发现部分解码匹配: {decoded} (原始: {ssid_hex})\")\n                found = True\n        except:\n            pass\n            \n    except Exception as e:\n        continue\n\nif not found:\n    print(\"未找到目标SSID\", file=sys.stderr)"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":343,"output":709,"cacheRead":42176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43228,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774531080174,"responseId":"4d2f6fc4-6992-4825-9a74-5294fde1aa97"}}
