{"type":"message","id":"589df6db","parentId":"cbc6bca5","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:18:56.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在启动tshark捕获SSID并传递给脚本。但我们需要捕获所有802.11帧的SSID字段，不仅仅是信标帧。让我使用更全面的过滤：捕获所有包含SSID字段的帧（类型0x00-0x04, 0x08, 0x05等）。实际上，SSID可能出现在多种帧类型中：信标(0x08)、探测请求(0x04)、探测响应(0x05)、关联请求(0x00)等。\n\n让我运行一个综合扫描：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vZrtKBKO3yYlscFLDeuU5rAy","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 60 tshark -i mon0 -Y \"wlan.ssid\" -T fields -e wlan.ssid 2>&1 | python3 /tmp/find_target_ssid.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":666,"output":310,"cacheRead":42496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43472,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774531114334,"responseId":"dbac6fe3-56b5-4046-b21c-b19662e11f54"}}
