{"type":"message","id":"4a23665b","parentId":"ffffc369","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:40:21.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"USB网卡是Ralink MT7601U芯片，驱动是mt7601u。这是USB无线网卡。现在需要检测它支持什么协议：802.11b/g/n? MT7601U支持802.11n（150Mbps），2.4GHz频段。可能需要查具体能力。用iw list可能需要安装。试试iwconfig。但可能未安装。用sudo iw list看看。先检查iw是否存在。用which iw。或者用sudo iw phy phy2 info。先看看iw是否安装。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DMGEl4gZ1LKeFoiAqU1kzFEZ","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which iw 2>/dev/null || echo \"iw not found\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":290,"output":289,"cacheRead":44608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774532389337,"responseId":"f2ff5e06-8ac0-471d-b8db-fd037057a72b"}}
